arts.ttl: Augsburg squeeze past Karlsruhe in penalty shootout win
arts.sum: Ruben Vargas' 124th minute equaliser saw Augsburg take Karlsruhe to penalties and then advance to the quarter-finals of the DFB-Pokal.
